^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Marty Bergen has invented what he calls OBAR bidding.  OBAR stands for "Over Opponents' Bid and Raise" which is exactly what this auction is. You can consider OBAR as a pre-balancing technique. If the auction goes 1x-p-2x, and you are short in the opponents' suit, you should strain to bid. Bidding does not show extra values, just balancing values.|
