NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The important thing is to be short in their suit. The three most common OBAR bids that is are:
1) Overcall a reasonable suit, even a good 5 card suit
2) Make a takeout double
3) Bid 2N which is takeout for the minors. It does not show 5/5. It can even be done with 4/4. Remember, partner should not assume extra values.|
